<refsynopsisdiv id='synopsis'>
<cmdsynopsis>
  <command>npm</command>    <arg choice='plain'><replaceable>test</replaceable></arg>
    <arg choice='opt'>-- <replaceable>&lt;args&gt;</replaceable></arg>
    <arg choice='plain'><replaceable>npm</replaceable></arg>
    <arg choice='plain'><replaceable>tst</replaceable></arg>
    <arg choice='opt'>-- <replaceable>&lt;args&gt;</replaceable></arg>
</cmdsynopsis>
</refsynopsisdiv>


<refsect1 id='description'><title>DESCRIPTION</title>
<para>This runs a package's "test" script, if one was provided.</para>

<para>To run tests as a condition of installation, set the <emphasis remap='B'>npat</emphasis> config to
true.</para>
</refsect1>

